title: Johnson has 2 TD receptions, leads Colts over Texans 27-20

> Texas Johnson has 2 TD receptions, leads Colts over Texans 27-20 Houston Texans' Brian Hoyer (7) and Jaelen Strong (11) celebrates after they connected on a touchdown pass against the Indianapolis Colts during the second half of an NFL football game Thursday, Oct. 8, 2015, in Houston.
